{"tid":1305514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好再寫「香港加油」！！","createTime":"2019-07-11T01:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T02:10:09.000Z","uid":22209,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"60687bb6626ac1925391dbb52b07d31dc25ff2ec","tid":1305514,"uid":22209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:09:23.000Z","msg":"無論香港人定外媒，為數唔少以為the bill is dead=撤咗。我明大家都想幫香港打氣，但淨係寫加油，連儂牆只會慢慢變成打氣區，幫唔到d街坊認清成件事其實仲未解決。<br />\n<br />\n大家如果再去連儂留言，希望可以集中返寫<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 五大訴求<br />\n2. 對the bill is dead嘅回應<br />\n3. 對警察暴力嘅睇法</span></span><br />\n<br />\np.s. 粗口留言、咒罵黑警死全家之類，我明大家都好嬲，你寫係連儂牆，部份潔癖街坊只會反感，累埋幫手睇站嘅戰友代你俾人鬧，連儂牆係和理優玩法，麻煩寫之前諗清楚。"},{"pid":"edf9f6dc6a60b849f0ac1c0870d34b511a140253","tid":1305514,"uid":22209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55745d8fc42229e551d6732f8cc16f802d6c4ec","tid":1305514,"uid":22209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc58927ca5a415200354d7cd585f4ec16c8ca9d3","tid":1305514,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:36:04.000Z","msg":"(置頂) 真普選抗爭三部曲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1303217\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1303217</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f1be821607fdc4b78d875e507dd78b6190ad5bc7","tid":1305514,"uid":22209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:50:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655a3cdf8bd80ff02023fa7b6a779dec9095bf52","tid":1305514,"uid":22209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc58927ca5a415200354d7cd585f4ec16c8ca9d3","tid":1305514,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:36:04.00